This directory contains Salt State files intended to be placed in /srv/salt for
the purpose of facilitating automation of SUSE Enterprise Storage (Ceph)
cluster deployments in AWS EC2.

More (and better) information on Salt States can be found here: 

http://docs.saltstack.com/en/latest/topics/tutorials/walkthrough.html

Directions for using these files to deploy Ceph using DeepSea are here:

https://github.com/smithfarm/ceph-auto-aws#deploying-with-deepsea

